00:02.619 --> 00:04.853
♪ Happy Birthday ♪

00:04.888 --> 00:06.354
Previously
on <i>Smash...</i>

00:06.389 --> 00:09.891
♪ Mr. director ♪

00:10.624 --> 00:14.160
- Dev?
- Will you marry me?

00:14.194 --> 00:15.161
I got a pilot.

00:15.195 --> 00:17.062
- Hang on!
- Pilot?

00:17.097 --> 00:18.998
My leading man
has left the show?

00:19.032 --> 00:20.633
Get me Michael Swift's
availability now.

00:20.668 --> 00:22.502
You tell them,
if he comes to Boston, I'm out.

00:22.536 --> 00:25.137
- Bloody hell.
- I'm nervous.

00:25.172 --> 00:28.407
You don't help me.
You don't talk to me!

00:28.441 --> 00:31.476
Ellis, can you
handle this, please?

00:31.511 --> 00:33.512
- I have everything on the line.
- So do I!

00:33.546 --> 00:35.847
- My name's Dev.
- Ivy.

